      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-1-a" mid="33" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(She can understand him?!)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>I understand what <FONT color=#a82424>Crazy Mad Bard</FONT> is trying to say.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-1-b" mid="34" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>But as you can see, I can't leave my store.<BR>If I could, I would have paid a visit to Mad Bard a long time ago.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-1-c" mid="35" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Wouldn't it be more meaningful if you went there yourself?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>……I have no choice but to ask you for a favour. Can you go and sincerely <FONT color=#2b2723>admire</FONT> the <FONT color=#a82424>thirteen alpacas</FONT> running in the plains on my behalf and tell me how you felt?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-1-d" mid="36" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>Geniuses like Bard don't give much explanation about the masterpieces they have created. I guess that's why he told me to see the alpacas for myself. But there's also a reason why critics and reviews exist in this world. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-2" mid="37" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>…Okay.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>People experience art and share their opinions with others to deepen the understanding about the work. So I hope you can have mercy on this hardworking teenager who's stuck here to earn a living and go and see the alpacas.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2006_wind_mad_bard-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="48"><![CDATA[<html>$Crazy Mad Bard$<BR>Are you here to hear the cries of the alpaca's souls?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>Then please go to the Blue Wind Plains. You'll see the alpacas running there.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2006_wind_mad_bard-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2006_wind_mad_bard-2-a" mid="53" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Why are those alpacas running like that?!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="52"><![CDATA[<html>$Crazy Mad Bard$<BR>Have you seen them? The alpacas that dashed through the plains as they grinded and spat on the fields?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2006_wind_mad_bard-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2006_wind_mad_bard-2-b" mid="55" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Grievance?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="54"><![CDATA[<html>$Crazy Mad Bard$<BR>Phew... What's making them run is... endless grievance!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2006_wind_mad_bard-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2006_wind_mad_bard-2-c" mid="57" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="56"><![CDATA[<html>$Crazy Mad Bard$<BR>Resentment for the humans who stole their fur!<BR>Outrage for the thieves who cut their meat!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2006_wind_mad_bard-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2006_wind_mad_bard-2-d" mid="59" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(I want to go back to Lagendia...)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="58"><![CDATA[<html>$Crazy Mad Bard$<BR>Their anger has built up over time and is finally exploding right here!<BR>
Hear their heartbeat! Feel their anger! Remember the clip-clop of their feet!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-3-a" mid="40" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Tell her what you saw.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>You're back! Did you see the alpacas?</html>]]></talk_question>
